{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-awesome-timeline-js","path":"/aaronhma/awesome-tensorflow-js/week/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Track Awesome List"}},"awesomeListMeta":{"readmeParsedAt":"2022-10-13T07:34:01.475Z","repo":"aaronhma/awesome-tensorflow-js","descriptionHTML":"<div>Awesome TensorFlow.js - A curated list of dedicated resources to master TensorFlow.js</div>","description":"Awesome TensorFlow.js - A curated list of dedicated resources to master TensorFlow.js","stargazerCount":137,"readmeItemsUpdatedTime":1617551124000,"category":"Computer Science"},"allAwesomeItem":{"nodes":[{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Learn</h2><h3>Books</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.apress.com/gp/book/9781484262726\">Practical TensorFlow.js</a> - Deep Learning in Web App Development by Juan De Dios Santos Rivera.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-04-04T15:45:24.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Learn</h2><h3>Books</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.apress.com/gp/book/9781484264171\">Practical Machine Learning in JavaScript</a> - TensorFlow.js for Web Developers by Charlie Gerard.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-04-04T15:45:24.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Learn</h2><h3>Books</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://amzn.to/3dR3vpY\">Learning Tensorflow.js: Powerful Machine Learning in JavaScript</a> - In this guide, author <a href=\"https://github.com/gantman\">Gant Laborde</a> provides a hands-on, end-to-end approach to TensorFlow.js fundamentals for a broad technical audience that includes data scientists, engineers, web developers, students, and researchers.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-03-08T21:26:52.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Learn</h2><h3>Tutorials</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://effectivemachinelearning.com/TensorFlow.js\">Effective TensorFlow.js</a> - TensorFlow.js tutorials and best practices.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-11-28T02:19:34.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Learn</h2><h3>Videos</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=X55m9eS5UFU\">Color Blind Tensors</a> - Manipulate image tensors to perceive color blindness, live coding.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-10-21T17:25:35.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Learn</h2><h3>Powered by TensorFlow.js</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://pose-animator-demo.firebaseapp.com/camera.html\">Pose Animator</a> - A tool to bring SVG characters to life in the browser via motion capture.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-09-09T03:49:52.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Learn</h2><h3>Powered by TensorFlow.js</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://lipsync.withyoutube.com/\">LipSync</a> - A web-based, playful, interactive experiences to lip sync to your favorite songs.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-09-09T03:49:52.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Learn</h2><h3>Powered by TensorFlow.js</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/tfjs-models/demos/body-pix/index.html\">BodyPix</a> - A real-time person and body-part segmentation in the browser.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-09-09T03:49:52.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Tools</h2><h3>Libraries</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://danfo.jsdata.org/\">Danfo.js</a> - High-performance, intuitive, and easy-to-use data structures for manipulating and processing structured data. (Inspired by Pandas)</li>","updatedAt":"2020-09-09T03:49:52.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Learn</h2><h3>Papers</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/1901.05350\">TensorFlow.js: Machine Learning for the Web and Beyond</a> - This paper describes the design, API, and implementation of TensorFlow.js, and highlights some of the impactful use cases.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-06-02T17:54:47.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Learn</h2><h3>Papers</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/1910.07402\">JSDoop and TensorFlow.js: Volunteer Distributed Web Browser-Based Neural Network Training</a> - The experimental results show that training a neural network in distributed web browsers is feasible and accurate, has a high scalability, and it is an interesting area for research.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-06-02T17:54:47.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Learn</h2><h3>Videos</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?reload=9&#x26;list=PLs6AluHXaQnjeI6jzDkpKXvbPj31i4GgF\">Official TensorFlow.js video series</a> - The YouTube content focuses on TensorFlow ecosystem updates.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-06-02T17:54:47.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Learn</h2><h3>Videos</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://youtu.be/iH9CS-QYmZs\">TensorFlow.js: ML for the web and beyond</a> - TensorFlow Dev Summit 2020.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-06-02T17:54:47.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Learn</h2><h3>Videos</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=y4pfTQJaUJU\">Rock Paper Scissors!</a> - Train Rock Paper Scissors on your machine and watch the results with your webcam!</li>","updatedAt":"2020-06-02T17:54:47.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Learn</h2><h3>Books</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.manning.com/books/deep-learning-with-javascript\">Deep Learning with JavaScript</a> - Learn to use TensorFlow.js to build deep learning models that run directly in the browser, master all the basics of deep learning and explore advanced concepts, like retraining existing models for transfer learning and image generation by Shanqing Cai, Stanley Bileschi, Eric D. Nielsen and Francois Chollet.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-06-02T17:54:47.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Learn</h2><h3>Books</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Hands-Machine-Learning-TensorFlow-js-applications/dp/1838821732\">Hands-On Machine Learning with TensorFlow.js</a> - A guide to building ML applications integrated with web technology using the TensorFlow.js library by Kai Sasaki.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-06-02T17:54:47.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Learn</h2><h3>Blog &#x26; Posts</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://blog.tensorflow.org/search?label=TensorFlow.js&#x26;max-results=20\">Official TensorFlow.js blog</a> - Covers building models in JavaS